## 3. Code Execution Sandbox — Security Model

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    CODE[LLM-Generated<br>Python Code] --> AST[AST Parsing<br>& Validation]
    AST -->|Blocked| REJECT[❌ Rejected<br>Unsafe code detected]
    AST -->|Passed| SUB[Subprocess<br>Isolation]
    SUB --> SAFE["Safe Globals Only:<br>pandas, numpy, math,<br>json, datetime, re,<br>statistics, collections"]
    SAFE --> TIMEOUT["60s Timeout Guard"]
    TIMEOUT -->|Success| RESULT[Normalized Results<br>tables, charts, text, stats]
    TIMEOUT -->|Timeout| FAIL[❌ TimeoutError]

    subgraph Blocked ["Blocked by AST Validator"]
        B1["Builtins: open, eval, exec,<br>__import__, exit, input"]
        B2["Modules: os, sys, subprocess,<br>socket, pathlib, shutil"]
        B3["Attributes: __class__, __dict__,<br>__globals__, system, popen"]
    end
```

