## 7. Suggested Improvements — Roadmap

### Phase 1: Critical Fixes (Must-Have)

| # | Improvement | Impact | Effort |
|---|-------------|--------|--------|
| 1 | **Add real authentication (Fixed)** — Implemented Supabase Auth with email/password signup, JWT verification, `@require_auth` decorator on all API routes. | Security | Medium |
| 2 | **Make state per-session (Fixed)** — Replaced `AppState` singleton with `SessionManager` + per-user `UserState`. All state keyed by `user_id` from JWT. Thread-safe. | Multi-user | Medium |
| 3 | **Add thread-safe caching (Fixed)** — `QueryCache` and `SessionManager` now use `threading.Lock()`. | Stability | Low |
| 4 | **Add rate limiting** — Use `Flask-Limiter` on `/api/chat` and `/api/suggest-questions` (e.g., 10 requests/minute). | Security | Low |
| 5 | **Make `API_BASE` dynamic (Fixed)** — Changed to `window.location.origin` in `core.js`. Works in any deployment. | Deployment | Low |
| 6 | **Add frontend request timeouts** — Use `AbortController` with 60s timeout on all fetch calls. | Reliability | Low |
| 7 | **Validate file size client-side (Fixed)** — Check `file.size` before uploading and show a warning. Cap at 10MB to match server config. | UX | Low |

